  <brief_title>Banded Sleeve Gastrectomy Improves Weight Loss Compared to Non-banded Sleeve: Mid-term Results</brief_title>
  <official_title>Banded Sleeve Gastrectomy Improves Weight Loss Compared to Non-banded Sleeve: Mid-term Results From a Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
